pageProduct.name: Swisse Skincare Argan Revitalising Eye Cream 15ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

With Argan Oil, Squalene, Grape Seed Oil, Caffeine and Guarana Seed Extract

Swisse Argan Revitalising Eye Cream is an ultra-hydrating formula that replenishes and refines the delicate under-eye area to prevent signs of premature aging for a more youthful and rested appearance

Suitable For: All skin types

Size: 15mL

Warnings

Test prior to use. In the unlikely event of a negative reaction, consult your medical practitioner

Ingredients

AQUA (Water)
Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil
Cetearyl Alcohol
Glycerin (Plant Derived)
Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil (Argan Oil)
Squalane
Cetearyl Olivate
Sorbitan Olivate
ALOE VERA Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Juice Powder
Caffeine
Menaquinone-7
Paullinia Cupana Seed Extract (Guarana)
Ubiquinone
Carthamus Tinctorius (Safflower) Seed Oil

Directions

Warm a small amount between fingers and pat into eye contour area.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 28°C.
